## Two Operating Modes

| Mode | Active Principles | When |
|------|-----------------|------|
| Exploration | Disrupt default patterns + Adversarial meta-agents + Reality anchoring | From Stage 0 until first external contact signal |
| Conviction | Force explicit output format + Reality anchoring | After external contact trigger |

The mode switch is external and inevitable. You cannot stay in exploration mode indefinitely because reality speaks first.

