## Content Layer

### The Dual Output Principle
Every Forge session run for decision-making becomes a content asset for free. Exploration output = publishable. Conviction output = private.

### Content Types Generated

| Type | Description |
|------|-------------|
| Forge Deliberations | Full structured debate showing agent tensions, convergence, conviction or honest uncertainty |
| Long-form Essays | Extended analysis distilled from deliberations |
| Agent Whitepapers | Each permanent agent produces its own longform POV piece on a topic — genuine insight with citations. Not regurgitation. |
| GEO Explainers | Most-searched questions in each domain, optimised for AI search engines and semantic discovery |

### Domain Authority Mechanism
Slop always has a conclusion. The Forge earns its conclusions or withholds them. That is the moat — and it is architectural, not a positioning choice. Audiences feel the difference even when they cannot articulate why.

